---
/**
 * ExternalServices — green sage section showing the consulting / advisory
 * services SuperBenefit offers to outside organizations and ecosystems.
 *
 * Three-column grid layout. Cream accents throughout — no gold, no orange.
 * Clean, confident, text-forward — like a design studio's capabilities page.
 */
---

<section id="services" class="external-services">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="ext-label" data-animate="fade-up">What We Offer</span>
    <h2 class="ext-heading" data-animate="fade-up">
      Services for organizations &amp; ecosystems
    </h2>
    <p class="ext-lede" data-animate="fade-up">
      Beyond our internal commons, SuperBenefit works with aligned organizations
      and networks to design governance, steward transitions, and build
      regenerative systems. Every engagement is collaborative — we learn as
      much as we share.
    </p>

    <div class="ext-services">
      <div class="ext-service" data-animate="fade-up" style="--stagger: 0ms">
        <h3 class="ext-service-heading">Strategic advisory</h3>
        <p class="ext-service-body">
          We help organizations design governance systems, steward community
          transitions, and navigate web3 adoption — from DAO legal wrappers
          to participatory budgeting and multi-stakeholder coordination.
        </p>
      </div>

      <hr class="ext-rule" aria-hidden="true">

      <div class="ext-service" data-animate="fade-up" style="--stagger: 100ms">
        <h3 class="ext-service-heading">Research &amp; strategy</h3>
        <p class="ext-service-body">
          Deep-dive research on coordination mechanisms, regenerative
          economics, and AI-augmented governance. We produce frameworks,
          reports, and actionable recommendations grounded in lived
          practice — not armchair theory.
        </p>
      </div>

      <hr class="ext-rule" aria-hidden="true">

      <div class="ext-service" data-animate="fade-up" style="--stagger: 200ms">
        <h3 class="ext-service-heading">Workshops &amp; facilitation</h3>
        <p class="ext-service-body">
          Tailored sessions for leadership teams, boards, and communities.
          We design and facilitate experiences that build shared
          understanding, surface latent tensions, and create alignment
          around complex decisions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="ext-footer" data-animate="fade-up">
      <a href="/services" class="ext-cta ext-cta-primary">
        See all services
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M5 12h14"></path><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a href="/contact" class="ext-cta ext-cta-secondary">
        Get in touch
      </a>
    </footer>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .external-services {
    background: var(--color-green-sage);
    padding-block: var(--space-xl) var(--space-2xl);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* ===== Label ===== */
  .ext-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-md);
  }

  /* ===== Heading ===== */
  .ext-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-md);
    max-width: 16ch;
  }

  /* ===== Lede ===== */
  .ext-lede {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.68;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 580px;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  /* ===== Services grid — three columns ===== */
  .ext-services {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .ext-service {
    /* no padding — column layout handles spacing via grid gap */
  }

  /* ===== Cream vertical rule between columns ===== */
  .ext-rule {
    display: none;
  }

  /* ===== Service heading ===== */
  .ext-service-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
  }

  /* ===== Service body ===== */
  .ext-service-body {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.65;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ===== Footer CTA ===== */
  .ext-footer {
    margin-block-start: var(--space-xl);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .ext-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5em;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    transition: opacity var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .ext-cta-primary {
    color: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .ext-cta-primary:hover {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .ext-cta-secondary {
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.7;
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .ext-cta-secondary:hover {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* ===== Stagger animation delay ===== */
  .ext-service[data-animate] {
    animation-delay: var(--stagger);
  }

  /* ===== Responsive ===== */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .ext-services {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .ext-services {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
